ist", "gallery_style_mobile": "carousel", "gallery_size": "large", "gallery_overflow": "3", "enable_video_looping": true, "enable_product_lightbox": true, "image_aspect_ratio": "portrait", "enable_multiple_variant_media": false, "enable_mobile_carousel_looping": true, "show_mobile_carousel_images_full_width": true, "hide_mobile_carousel_dots": false, "enable_gift_card_recipient": true, "enable_animation": true}}, "product_tabs": {"type": "product-tabs", "blocks": {"tab_description": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Description", "heading_column_1": "What Makes It Special", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>A quiet encounter. Two points in gentle harmony \u2014 a luminous freshwater pearl meets a softly glowing moonstone, each cradled in organic gold forms that feel like they grew rather than were made.</p><p>At just 12mm, these are the earrings you reach for when you want something effortless but unmistakably intentional. The moonstone shifts between blue and silver depending on the light. The pearl glows warm. Together they create a conversation between cool and warm that changes throughout the day.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_details": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Details & Materials", "heading_column_1": "Specifications", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> 14k yellow gold</li><li><strong>Stones:</strong> Freshwater pearl (6mm \u00d7 2), Indian moonstone (0.64 ct total)</li><li><strong>Total Length:</strong> 12mm</li><li><strong>Weight:</strong> Featherlight \u2014 perfect for all-day wear</li><li><strong>Closure:</strong> Post with butterfly back</li><li><strong>Collection:</strong> Echoes</li></ul>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_care": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Care", "heading_column_1": "Jewelry Care", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Pieces:</strong> Put jewelry on last, take it off first. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Store in the provided pouch. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals. Pearls benefit from being worn \u2014 natural skin oils maintain their luster.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_shipping": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every piece is handcrafted to order in NYC. Please allow 3\u20134 weeks for production. Free insured shipping on all orders. Signature required on delivery. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when your piece ships.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos for repair or replacement.</p>", "page_for_content_column_2": "", "custom_liquid_column_2": "", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["tab_description", "tab_details", "tab_care", "tab_shipping"], "settings": {"tab_alignment": "left", "tab_spacing": 40, "font_choice": "ff-heading", "tab_font_size": "fs-body-150", "auto_collapse_rows": false, "background_color": "", "text_color": "#000000", "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-bottom-only"}}, "multi-column": {"type": "multi-column", "blocks": {}, "block_order": [], "disabled": true, "settings": {"title": "", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-3-base", "subheading": "", "heading_alignment": "left", "content_vertical_alignment": "center", "content_background_padding": "large", "columns": "3", "column_spacing": 4, "row_spacing": 28, "column_alignment": "center", "enable_slider_mobile": false, "columns_mobile": "1", "column_spacing_mobile": 4, "row_spacing_mobile": 4, "column_alignment_mobile": "center", "background_behind_columns": false, "background_color": "#f5f3f0", "text_color": "#3d352f", "button_background_color": "#000000", "button_text_color": "#ffffff", "enable_animation": true, "divider_style": "none", "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-top-bottom"}}, "image-hero": {"type": "image-hero", "blocks": {"accent": {"type": "accent", "settings": {"accent": "ECHOES COLLECTION"}}, "heading": {"type": "heading", "settings": {"title": "Duo", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-display-2"}}}, "block_order": ["accent", "heading"], "settings": {"image_aspect": "custom", "desktop_height": 60, "mobile_height": 65, "focal_point": "center", "mobile_focal_point": "center", "media_link": "", "text_position": "flex-end_flex-end", "text_position_mobile": "center_center", "text_color": "#f5f5f5", "button_background_colo